|--------|---------|------|
| cosmic.board | CosmicBoard | 7777 |
| loopify.sam | Segment Loop | 8088 |
| prism.ai | RichPrism AI | 9393 |

## Troubleshooting
```bash
# Check domain resolution
ping yourdomain.local

# Test nginx routing
curl -H "Host: yourdomain.local" http://127.0.0.1

# Flush DNS cache
sudo dscacheutil -flushcache
```

